  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nIf you have some custom tokens on your account, you will not see balance just after enabling token in asset.\r\nFor fetching balance logout is required.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ncan see balance\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n0; balance is fetched after relogin\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Restore account with some custom tokens (i.e. WEENUS, [how to get them ](https://ethereum.stackexchange.com/questions/38743/where-can-i-find-erc20-token-faucets-for-testing))\r\n- Go to wallet > Manage assets > Add custom token > Add WEENUS\r\n- Wait for several minutes\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nigthly 10/12/2019\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
